        "High reactivity = Hard to extract (Electrolysis). Low reactivity = Easy (Heating)."
      ]
    },
    "selfCheckQuestions": [
      "Can Copper displace Zinc from Zinc Sulfate?"
    ],
    "quickSummary": [
      "Metals react differently; the series predicts these reactions."
    ],
    "keyTerms": [
      "Reactivity Series",
      "Displacement",
      "Ionic Compounds"
    ],
    "fillInTheBlanks": [
